keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
unmap <c-e>
unmap <c-y>
unmap [[
unmap ]]

map J scrollPageDown
map K scrollPageUp
map [ goPrevious
map ] goNext
map F LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab
map , visitPreviousTab
map . nextTab
